videos.headline: Williams breaks free for 82-yard TD run
videos.description: Utah RB Joe Williams turns on the jets and goes 82 yards for the touchdown to extend the Utes' lead to 28-20 over Arizona State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams breaks free for 82-yard TD run) 2016/11/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: White hauls in ASU TD, Sun Devils two-point attempt fails
videos.description: Tim White makes the back-shoulder TD catch to get Arizona State within two of Utah, but the Sun Devils misfire on the two-point conversion attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (White hauls in ASU TD, Sun Devils two-point attempt fails) 2016/11/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams fires fourth TD for Utah
videos.description: Troy Williams hits Raelon Singleton in the end zone from 24 yards out to extend Utah's lead to 35-26 over Arizona State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams fires fourth TD for Utah) 2016/11/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pick-six puts Utah up big
videos.description: Chase Hansen picks off Manny Wilkins and returns it 34 yards for a Utah touchdown to put the Utes up 42-26 over Arizona State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pick-six puts Utah up big) 2016/11/10 ESHEET
